      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KODA (1) turned in a modest effort most recently when fifth at Sandown over 515m behind Shade Of Pale (30.29) in a Grade 5. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Can discover winning form. DR. FANATICAL (6) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (33.39) at this track behind Lakeview Ian in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from five attempts. Leading chance. WHISKY BELLA (2) had been in super honest form hitting the frame two times on end before finishing fourth (25.72) at Ballarat last time. Deserves plenty of respect. EAGLE BREAD (7) will need to run right up to last start to feature again.",
